{
  "stem": "16473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And mother just made that decision, that that was too inhumane.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "A woman had risked her life, her daughter was already shot, so she gave up her rations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The question was, what did I remember, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's, well, I suppose along with this comes the fact that when the Nazis came and occupied our building, they used one part of the building for their soldiers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I remember distinctly that I heard Nazis talking about throwing babies against the wall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was just sort of-- I was standing, I mean, I know where I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a staircase, they were on the staircase, and I was just sort of standing there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told my mother that I had heard that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And mother said, no, you didn't, you didn't hear that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, yes, I did, that's what they said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for the most part, you know, you asked me was I told, were things explained.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think any of that was done because reality couldn't be looked in the face.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if you didn't look at it, it didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, sort of.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you know this was happening to the babies because they were Jewish?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I knew I had to be afraid for my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a neighbor in that building who made innuendos to my mother that he knew that we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he kept her frightened for her life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew about it, and I knew that we needed to be frightened, you know, for our life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's something that I forgot to say, but I just want to throw it in here because this idea of not looking reality in the face.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
